title.rendered: Box of 100, High-Quality Disposable Isolation Gown Level 2 25GSM

content.rendered:
Suitable for medical practitioners, allied health clinicians and dental clinics. Immediate delivery – stock available now. These are high-quality disposable gowns.

  • SMS Level 2 Impervious Gown
  • 25GSM
  • Elastic wrist
  • Waist and Neck tie
  • 120cm x 140cm
  • Manufactured to ISO EN13485:2016
